title: Break Through The Barriers Of The Past | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Break Through The Barriers Of The Past | Victoria Osteen
description:
Don't allow old wounds to limit your future. If you'll let go of the hurt, God will restore everything you've lost. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. 

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
